name: The Temptation Vasco - 24x7 Complete Food Shop

reviews.review_text: I was here today and must say that this place is absolutely a delight in Vasco. Its authentic Goan masalas, its freshly baked breads, muffins, snacks, cakes and pastries are simply irresistible. If you are in South Goa close to dabolim airport or in vasco or nearby, you must make a point to visit this.

I like the ambience. The staff is friendly and the ambience is peaceful. We met a cute kitty as well.
The food though was not worth it in terms of quantity against the amount we paid. For example, I ordered a Veg Cutlet wrap/bun for Rs. 150 and the quantity or the filling wasn't just enough. So I think this beautiful place can work on enhancing the quantity varying with price. The chocolate cheese, amounting to Rs 70 cake could have been better as well.

This is one of the oldest and authentic outlet. They have retained their quality and expanded their outlets with trendy set ups. You get variety of sandwiches,  bread rolls , fresh bread and cakes. They have good veg options too. One suggestion- plz keep two seperate grills and ovens for veg and non veg preparation. Rest all is awesome

description:
### The Temptation Vasco: A Tantalizing Culinary Retreat in Vasco da Gama

Nestled in the heart of Vasco da Gama, *The Temptation Vasco - 24x7 Complete Food Shop* is a culinary haven boasting an impressive overall rating of 4 stars from a solid count of 2,300 reviews. Frequent mentions of their delightful **shakes** (92), scrumptious **pastries** (69), and hearty **rolls** (58) reflect the restaurant's commitment to offering a diverse menu. What's more, the venue has become a popular choice for **birthday** celebrations, making it a cherished spot for joyous gatherings.

### Ambiance & Design

Stepping into *The Temptation Vasco*, guests are greeted with a harmonious blend of modern décor and cozy furnishings. The ambiance is both vibrant and serene, making it an inviting choice for casual dining or quick bites. The soft lighting and neatly arranged seating areas perfectly complement the establishment's charm. A delightful surprise that visitors have noted is the friendly presence of a cute kitty, enhancing the warm and welcoming atmosphere. Customer photos depict a clean and spacious interior, punctuated by colorful displays of baked goods and pastries that beckon sweet-toothed patrons.

![Ambiance](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdmvVH-BG_-YHQ2k9WJ2pzD5ZNl_12oxc_RyQ0GdNSX3YmYR5f7y9FuS2leCW8_AcihTCjq-OqN-0Wha_ozHC1rKWd-jNUXSHw8KepS-JcU05j6Sq-2Ue-iUrhjrAzhQHPIhrwyC=w375-h281-p)

### Menu & Culinary Experience

With a menu that showcases the best of Goan cuisine, *The Temptation Vasco* features an array of **freshly baked breads, muffins, snacks, cakes**, and of course, the standout **shakes** that keep customers coming back for more. Signature items include their famous **Veg Cutlet roll**, though some guests have noted that the portion sizes may leave a little to be desired in relation to their prices. However, the quality of the food remains undisputed, with many praising the authentic Goan flavors. 

The bakery section is particularly appealing, with delectable pastries and cakes on display, all crafted with care. Visually, the dishes served are a treat for the eyes, with vibrant colors and exquisite presentations that are sure to entice any foodie. For those needing dietary accommodations, there are ample vegetarian options alongside flavorful non-vegetarian choices.

![Food Selection](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdlALpTOW3tLOqXb773vW93uHl-VXtEEEybRRtf52rlwniaJfjCemSanoiLtGdP3ExPQsla2DW2qL9n6CuksNfTZOXSoBz6V5e1iTgGFjHIfk8OOSg3Anwey0g4jLfRihDD-AvsSSw=w375-h281-p)

### Customer Experience & Service

Guests have consistently reported friendly and efficient service at *The Temptation Vasco*. The staff's attentiveness combined with their welcoming demeanor creates a pleasant dining experience that feels personal. While reservations aren’t explicitly mentioned, the casual format of the shop likely supports walk-ins, making it accessible for those needing a quick meal or craving something sweet at any hour.

### Popularity & Reviews

There's a palpable buzz surrounding this eatery, with customer reviews painting a largely positive picture. The restaurant's rich history as an authentic outlet combined with its modernization has earned it a loyal customer base. However, constructive feedback from repeat diners suggests that improving quantity to match pricing could elevate the experience even further.

![Pastries](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdmRapbh8rzp7q2Y0OFaWh8IbMbeIxfd8elynsvfGxBea917hNGfqzwQDwuKBCa7q7U70pQ0IdNGBbKUZ46CEdMbsr0P67IgTZjKqlWGVK2hwK6VuaVUkYHwHzSvIsFDctrrLMa7=w375-h563-p)

### Conclusion

In summary, *The Temptation Vasco* stands out as a delightful destination for those seeking to indulge in Goan flavors and satisfying sweets. Whether it's for a quick snack or a celebratory birthday feast, this popular eatery is ready to tempt your tastebuds with its rich offerings. For anyone in or around Vasco da Gama, this spot is certainly worth a visit.
